  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><span class=\"fontstyle0\">The domain of fire allows the magus to freely manipulate this unstable element. Whether the fire summoned is a harbinger of destruction, a purifying force or a source of comfortable warmth is left to the judgment of the magus.<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\"><strong>KNOWN SPELLS</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">When you choose this secret, you learn the @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.EOmsUcFQJTfG2oio]{Fire Bolt}and @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.eCPQuQkIabFKTl9u]{Produce Flame}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> </span><span class=\"fontstyle0\">cantrips, and when you gain a level in the secret you learn the corresponding spells indicated in the following table:<br /></span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>Cantrips: </strong>@Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.EOmsUcFQJTfG2oio]{Fire Bolt}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.eCPQuQkIabFKTl9u]{Produce Flame}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>1st level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.22dPoeXfaaAv4K3h]{Hellish Rebuke}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.5SuJewoa1CRWaj1F]{Burning Hands}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>2nd level:</strong></span><span class=\"fontstyle3\"> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.7u2obDvuvtZBkTfq]{Scorching Ray}, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.2yHXEcrRbadZDr5M]{Heat Metal}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>3rd level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.ztgcdrWPshKRpFd0]{Fireball}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.j8NtLXOOJ3GAKF8I]{Protection from Energy}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>4th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.X3DrXgxjwI2dvkD6]{Wall of Fire}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.avD5XUtkBPQQR97c]{Fire Shield}<br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\" style=\"font-size:10pt\"><strong>5th level:</strong> @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.5e1xTohkzqFqbYH4]{Flame Strike}</span><span class=\"fontstyle3\">, @Compendium[dnd5e.spells.Item.1LkZvINag7KqBmDR]{Conjure Elemental(Fire)}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>MYSTERIES</strong></span> <br style=\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:normal;orphans:2;text-align:-webkit-auto;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:2;word-spacing:0px;-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px\" />@Compendium[world.profession-features.7udQoXOYoN4YZ54E]{Founding Mystery: Pyrokinesis}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.5L3KnR6mB6oZZGWN]{Major Mystery: Playing with Fire}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.1tEjRyupjusFw1KZ]{Greater Mystery: Flare Up}</p><p>@Compendium[world.profession-features.W5Z9RewFcLBHi84h]{Universal Mystery: Flame Form}</p><p><span class=\"fontstyle0\"><strong>METAMAGIC OF THE SECRET</strong><br /></span><span class=\"fontstyle2\">When you reach 3rd level in this Secret, you became able to modify the spells they can cast, adapting them to your current needs, and learns the following metamagic options.</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.ljBsmjtT7u9AHiWI]{Metamagic: Empowered Spell}</span></p><p><span class=\"fontstyle2\">@Compendium[world.profession-features.whLFvYadGWywTXMH]{Metamagic: Careful Spell}</span></p><p> </p>",
      "chat": "",
      "unidentified": ""
    },
    "source": "Historia Manuale pagina: 146",
